title: Microsoft Office 2016 Professional Plus X64
description:
Microsoft Office 2016 Professional Plus X64 (c) Microsoft Corp
Office Professional 2016 helps you create, present, communicate, and
publish professional-looking documents with time-saving features, a new
modern look, and built-in collaboration tools. Save your work in the
cloud on OneDrive and access it from anywhere

Requirements

Microsoft Windows 7 or higher
1 gigahertz (GHz) or faster x86-bit or x64-bit processor
2 GB RAM
3.0 GB available disk space
